{"tid":2160332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭月娥退回劍橋院士名銜    學院︰多謝關心","createTime":"2020-08-17T01:03:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T04:15:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"544068a5656c074785ec5b7fc166d1c93ad35098","tid":2160332,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:03:01.000Z","msg":"沃爾森學院早前稱會審視林鄭的名銜，林鄭前晚在個人fb專頁發文，稱學院受到當地政客及傳媒的壓力，提出毫無事實根據、道聽塗說的指控，包括偏離學術自由和言論表達自由的原則等，個人雖「對這些虛名從不看重」，但對此感失望，不欲與學院有任何聯繫，決定退回有關名銜。<br />\n<br />\n學院其後發表聲明，稱關注林鄭近期在保障人權和言論自由方面的言行，而林鄭以放棄名銜回應。<br />\n <br />\n　　學院原定下月會檢討她的名銜，但目前不會繼續，亦不會再有其他回應。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/mobile/tc/lifestyle/internationalaffairs/news/67408</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4e2d85f0aa6252f4522e7b37cadf150e64767b2a","tid":2160332,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:05:36.000Z","msg":"人民日報--劍橋大學違反港區國安法，林鄭月娥有必要追究到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54db66949be9111a7b08c04b27d8e0ad968f39ec","tid":2160332,"uid":7763,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DAvN5Lo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDAvN5Lo.jpg&h=9d4e9999&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6286375bc7b9a18c13e2f319a02ccd0528baeac7","tid":2160332,"uid":264983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T04:15:58.000Z","msg":"777"}]}